{"tid":2046885,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利擬容許旅客入境 促請民眾繼續保持社交距離","createTime":"2020-06-01T16:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T03:46:26.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57cc6d0cf62bdc65258ca926ceff9d34143dbbbc","tid":2046885,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"意大利擬容許旅客入境 促請民眾繼續保持社交距離<br />\n2020-06-01 HKT 23:38<br />\n<br />\n意大利進一步放寬防疫措施，計劃當地周三容許外來旅客入境，民眾亦可恢復跨區流動。<br />\n<br />\n當地一名醫生聲言，新冠病毒已經在意大利消失，引發爭議，政府要求民眾繼續保持警惕，形容當地正處防控關鍵時刻，必須避免疫情再度爆發，促請民眾保持社交距離，出外必需佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n意大利累計確診23萬宗新型肺炎，累計超過3萬3千人死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529633-20200601.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529633-20200601.htm&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns87PkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=965ac0f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529633-20200601.htm&h=e5c1b714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529633-20200601.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">此措施看來亦適用於香港，可惜從意大利回港要強制隔離</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>備註: &nbsp;在6月1日，意大利新增確診200宗，多60人死亡</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"37e9585000634cdd10b09cdea198f39aaaba3a1d","tid":2046885,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"好消息當然要推啦"}]}